<header class="page-header container">
  <h1>Contact &amp; support</h1>
  <p class="lead">We need a working inbox before Plaid production review and public launch. Replace placeholders below.</p>
</header>

<div class="container prose section section--tight">
  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p><strong>General &amp; product support:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">{{ site.supportEmail }}</a></p>
  <p><strong>Privacy &amp; data requests:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">{{ site.supportEmail }}</a> <em>[Add a dedicated privacy inbox if required by policy.]</em></p>

  <h2>Mailing address</h2>
  <p>{{ site.companyLegalName }}<br>{{ site.address }}</p>

  <h2>Response time</h2>
  <p class="muted">Target: business-day acknowledgment within <strong>[X]</strong> hours and resolution or next steps within <strong>[Y]</strong> days. <em>[Set real SLAs.]</em></p>

  <h2>Bug reports</h2>
  <p class="muted">Include device model, iOS version, and steps to reproduce. Do not send bank passwords or full card numbers by email.</p>

  <div class="callout">
    Update <code>website/src/_data/site.json</code> with your real domain, entity name, address, and support email, then redeploy.
  </div>
</div>
